{"tid":504194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）男嬰嘴塞紙被放膠袋綁死結　6℃低溫棄垃圾堆","createTime":"2017-12-19T16:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T07:49:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2743d08e16941d4701385ec9f3899caab96dcb8a","tid":504194,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"穗嬰嘴塞紙被放膠袋綁死結　6℃低溫棄垃圾堆<br />\n12月19日(二) 21:47   <br />\n東網電視<br />\n<br />\n廣州市區連日來最低氣溫只得攝氏6度左右，在如此天寒地凍之時，周一（18日）有市民在垃圾堆發現一名棄嬰，男嬰被發現時全身赤裸，只有黑色的膠袋包裹着，連臍帶都未剪斷，嘴裏還塞着紙巾，皮膚和手腳均冷得發白。 <br />\n<br />\n發現男嬰的李姓男子表示，當日早上8時許他與同事途經白雲區同德圍橫滘村，聽到垃圾堆中傳出聲音，剛開始他還以為聽到貓叫，「後來覺得不對勁，應該是小孩的哭喊」。於是他從垃圾堆撥弄幾下，始發現一個黑色膠袋內裝着一名男嬰。 <br />\n<br />\n李男又指，膠袋綁了一個死結，空氣難以進入，男嬰就這樣被埋在1米高的垃圾堆中不知多久。他看到男嬰的皮膚已凍得發白，立即脫下自己的羽絨給他保暖，並帶男嬰前往附近的醫院治療。經醫生檢查，男嬰是個剛出生的嬰兒，幸好身上僅有幾處皮外傷並無大礙。 <br />\n<br />\n廣州白雲警方周二（19日）通報，經現場走訪調查，警方暫未證實男嬰的身份，遂按程序將他送至社會福利院。男嬰生命體徵正常，但因體溫過低，已被警方轉送至醫院治療。而警方正全力尋找男嬰的家屬。"},{"pid":"281aeab49f9c4b52efa51471e9b92d6d3340165c","tid":504194,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171219/mobile/bkncn-20171219214742913-1219_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171219%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171219214742913-1219_05011_001.html&d=FFJHfFyzXKEE2yn2KHul8sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f13a074f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171219/mobile/bkncn-20171219214742913-1219_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6a341f3abf3eaeb660b5dedaff0e64675ee243c","tid":504194,"uid":58316,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"趁咁細個離開人世仲好啦唔使做大陸人"},{"pid":"fbcc1163044136d87395d27d52f10a3a257ca9e6","tid":504194,"uid":44257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>趁咁細個離開人世仲好啦唔使做大陸人</blockquote><br />\n人性vs現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1557152318287b8a82b61ab0e61f70470d53a2","tid":504194,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:49:36.000Z","msg":"究極救佢會係好事定壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a2f4d720683b08f1bd5c7451693ab35d77d64f","tid":504194,"uid":136760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟救佢會係好事定壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3758a2302f950cf311e03c3e2444c5800e603a58","tid":504194,"uid":30067,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究極救佢會係好事定壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廿年後落來香港偷野搶劫殺人"},{"pid":"d40b8e8e66ee2b8eae53662886e04669781e73d8","tid":504194,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究極救佢會係好事定壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該壞事多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0276ddaff310843964f09d0bec7f4f0e85272d","tid":504194,"uid":13149,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:35:57.000Z","msg":"人地登出緊個game 做咩同人取消登出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fadd576fe1ce0c3ba766ae9b0c4f2dd0422875","tid":504194,"uid":120772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T18:47:23.000Z","msg":"咁命硬 可能真係命不該絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61567a3146422c823c1beba83e83b4b69b8ae09","tid":504194,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T21:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b8a26c1267ffc88b476e2bd350edc79c905947","tid":5